Overview
========
Original problem link: https://cs50.harvard.edu/x/2020/psets/1/mario/more/

The goal of Mario is simple. Prompt the user for a height, and print out two pyramids with a gap of 2 and with the height that the user wishes. The height must be between 1 and 8 inclusive, and if the user does not provide a valid input, they must be reprompted continuously until they provide a valid one.


Example
=======
$ ./mario
Height: 20
Height: a
Height: 7
